Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:01.47,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侍从兵 江·涛一等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.84,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Planet "Econia"
